# =============================================================================
# FASO DIGITALISATION — Trivy CVE Acceptance List
# =============================================================================
# Format : CVE-XXXX-XXXXX
# Each entry MUST have:
#   - Justification
#   - Accepted-by (team/person)
#   - Expiry (max 30 days from acceptance date)
#
# Process: open a security ticket, get approval from security lead,
# then add entry here. Remove on expiry or when fix is available.
# =============================================================================

