# =============================================================================
# HOW TO ADD A NEW EXCEPTION
# =============================================================================
# 1. Create security ticket referencing the CVE
# 2. Document mitigation or compensating control
# 3. Get approval from security lead
# 4. Uncomment the CVE line below the comments
# 5. Set Expiry <= accepted-date + 30 days
# 6. Schedule a calendar reminder to review before expiry
# =============================================================================
